<p><b>How to fill out a mood chart?</b> Determine how many times a day you would like to chart. Create a special spot for each time-frame in your journal and leave 3 to 4 lines open beneath the time spot. Then, leave a number of lines clear at the bottom of each page for additional notes on your mood, energy, stressors and/or behaviors for that day.</p>